Hi.

Stop this nonsense. 

The Domain name system is not going to change the way it does names.

If you want to argue about the right way to do names there are plenty of
important conferences to go to, and even a Task Force of the DSAB.  If you
have learned from the errors of the Domain Name System, write a paper, get
published, become a famous systems consultant; but please, don't argue about
it on this list.

--jon.

